{"tid":2367251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國北方沙塵天氣致空氣嚴重污染","createTime":"2021-01-15T07:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T07:55:46.000Z","uid":289214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d06deda14094c801cb43b8a1368dc7c621f9fae9","tid":2367251,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"中國北方沙塵天氣致空氣嚴重污染 專家：2002年以來最早出現<br />\n<br />\n中國北方地區持續受沙塵影響，多地出現重度及以上程度空氣污染。中國環境監測總站監測顯示，今早（14日）6時，河北張家口，山西太原、大同、陽泉、臨汾，內蒙古呼和浩特等多個城市受沙塵影響，中國環境監測總站監測顯示，「空氣質量指數」達500，代表空氣嚴重污染。受沙塵影響，京津冀及周邊地區、長三角北部等地有浮塵天氣，空氣以輕至中度污染為主，河北西部沿山、河南北部部分城市有重度污染。<br />\n<br />\n內地中新網報道，是次出現大範圍沙塵天氣，主要是因為冷空氣頻繁。國家大氣污染防治攻關聯合中心組織專家指出，這是2021年首次沙塵天氣，也是自2002年以來出現時間最早的一次。冷空氣頻繁是形成此次的主要原因。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">香港又吹D污染物上去</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20210114/s00004/1610615098883/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%8c%97%e6%96%b9%e6%b2%99%e5%a1%b5%e5%a4%a9%e6%b0%a3%e8%87%b4%e7%a9%ba%e6%b0%a3%e5%9a%b4%e9%87%8d%e6%b1%a1%e6%9f%93-%e5%b0%88%e5%ae%b6-2002%e5%b9%b4%e4%bb%a5%e4%be%86%e6%9c%80%e6%97%a9%e5%87%ba%e7%8f%be?fbclid=IwAR0ZHZldQO_NFjXQhK3tAkLzJ5aKOqBzdfx0alPvFA2NC5e-44rdCX3qZls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20210114%2Fs00004%2F1610615098883%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%258c%2597%25e6%2596%25b9%25e6%25b2%2599%25e5%25a1%25b5%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e6%25b0%25a3%25e8%2587%25b4%25e7%25a9%25ba%25e6%25b0%25a3%25e5%259a%25b4%25e9%2587%258d%25e6%25b1%25a1%25e6%259f%2593-%25e5%25b0%2588%25e5%25ae%25b6-2002%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e4%25be%2586%25e6%259c%2580%25e6%2597%25a9%25e5%2587%25ba%25e7%258f%25be%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ZHZldQO_NFjXQhK3tAkLzJ5aKOqBzdfx0alPvFA2NC5e-44rdCX3qZls&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=43c10d72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2